{"type": "article", "id": 43342, "title": "爱尔兰旅游局做了一条 77 米长的《权游》挂毯，你认得啥？", "description": "还好不是绣的原著，不然更长。", "date": "2017-07-24T10:38:07Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 65, "name": "营销"}, {"id": 1203, "name": "权力的游戏"}, {"id": 42638, "name": "爱尔兰旅游局"}], "category": 18, "column": 31, "author": 103970, "comment_count": 15, "praise_count": 131, "image": "img/article/article_show/20170724174939EurQRvsqMdzg1oSA.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">每次《权力的游戏》开播，剧中魔幻的取景地总是会引人关注。上周一的首播集创造了七季以来最高的实时收视人数，打破了 HBO 的收视纪录，相信很多人都注意到了客串的黄老板和艾莉亚的对手戏，而他们所待的幽静森林，正是北爱尔兰的安特里姆郡。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201707241751227SvTrydWnIqBDebZ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.516667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170724175123V70RYS6JLQwHMbIN.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>北爱尔兰自从《权游》热播以来，就变成了一个剧迷们朝圣的热门目的地。这里有临冬城堡的沃德城堡庄园和沃德城堡塔，也有布满姿态各异树木的安特里姆郡的黑暗树篱。 </p><p>为了吸引全球各地的《权游》粉丝来北爱尔兰一睹究竟，爱尔兰旅游局最近又和广告公司阳狮伦敦携手，制作了一条长达 77 米的挂毯，把《权力的游戏》前六季的诸多重要场景，按照故事的顺序都绣在了上面。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170724175204I9qVchwSa4E7xvOF.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.560345\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170724175204K81DXLTWHxGZRrnp.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.551724\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>这条贝叶挂毯风格的《权游》挂毯编织展现了 100 多个不同的场景，花了 9 个星期时间来创作。在上面，你能看到“血色婚礼”、“君临决斗”，也能看到琼·雪诺被刺死、布兰被詹姆推下塔顶的种种场景。 </p><p>目前，这条挂毯正在北爱尔兰首府贝尔法斯特的阿尔斯特博物馆展出。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170724175221tV12A0i5aNrTWYBE.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.604990\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201707241752454KAE13M7njhaI0Fg.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.200000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170724175246W47Ryn0KsDXYhlcG.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666320\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170724175248ZfDr4OsaJWXkFoBx.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.604990\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170724175247yvdEwYz5PhcIefq3.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.570686\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170724175248uX87vKYdOZbakPFD.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.589397\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170724175249q5RvEM8eCd3GSOcg.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666320\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170724175250WxzMdTuaBnS3vCoj.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.744283\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201707241752503jwNI7f26HyXdvLJ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666320\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170724175250uet2NIqkmHQSM765.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666320\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170724175251QiBodMFPTHEDfSyN.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666320\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170724175251wHc0WAygJNQFkl1f.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666320\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170724175251Uu1Wg47zcAQ8YvEZ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666320\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170724175338XsUP2DqbfnTC4ABM.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666320\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170724175431BxnfW0KyCugLdEmw.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.756757\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>题图来自爱尔兰旅游局</p>"}